				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$\mathbb {Z}_{p}$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M4"><mml:msub><mml:mrow><mml:mi>ℤ</mml:mi></mml:mrow><mml:mrow><mml:mi>p</mml:mi></mml:mrow></mml:msub></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="13059_2021_2553_Article_IEq2.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula> and added to parameters matrix <italic>M</italic><sub><italic>i</italic></sub> using modular addition over <inline-formula id="IEq3"><alternatives><tex-math id="M5">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
